{"id": 1937, "genre": 1001, "title": "说起来，你真的做过职业规划这件事吗？", "description": "你的职业路径是自己决定的？参考别人的？还是一直在任其发展地放养？(题图来自：GIPHY)", "record_count": 2034, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170929180817afXDbgilMdvrKqFh.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-10-09T03:00:02Z", "options": [{"id": 240640, "content": "满脑子只有赚钱，规划什么的不重要", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 810660}, {"id": 241152, "content": "弹幕形式很好", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 955811}, {"id": 240641, "content": "随波逐流，水到渠成，还真没动过脑子", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1148676}, {"id": 240642, "content": "冥想", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 847302}, {"id": 240643, "content": "规划大都是长辈的意见 真正自己有强烈意愿的没多少", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1073283}, {"id": 240644, "content": "计划赶不上变化快", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 663008}, {"id": 241156, "content": "前一天规划好，跟人一聊，又改了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1151285}, {"id": 240645, "content": "没有哦\n然后到一定时候就开始后悔没有规划了", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1130402}, {"id": 240901, "content": "从来都是见机行事", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1076634}, {"id": 240646, "content": "没", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 999188}, {"id": 240647, "content": "计划赶不上变化，何况没有计划……", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1038091}, {"id": 240648, "content": "其实是不知道要做什么。知道的想很大，不知道怎么做到", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 730334}, {"id": 240904, "content": "一脸蒙逼ing～", "image": "img/option/option/20171010134203FMwbYTNfXhn6yPdD", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1151209}, {"id": 240649, "content": "规划都是跟着变化的节奏临时规划，计划赶不上变化", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 372727}, {"id": 240650, "content": "放养，收钱卖命", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1086101}, {"id": 240651, "content": "理想很丰满，现实很骨感。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1112144}, {"id": 314636, "content": "大一有这样的作业，我正在写。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1500723}, {"id": 240653, "content": "总想着去哪个大公司，结果网申都不敢投", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 64488}, {"id": 243214, "content": "理想跟现实，不在同一层次上", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1157715}, {"id": 240655, "content": "其实心里应该有个大概的谱，想往什么方向发展，对应需要补充什么样的技能和经验 ~ 但并不是写哪一年能发展到什么岗位的东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 882331}, {"id": 240657, "content": "其实心里应该有个大概的谱，想往什么方向发展，对应需要补充什么样的技能和经验 ~ 但并不是写哪一年能发展到什么岗位的东西", "image": "img/option/option/20171009125713zjiw5LsCV9QISqTc", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 882331}, {"id": 240658, "content": "站在山脚隐隐约约看见山顶有座凉亭山雾环绕，迎风吟诗的好去处，边走边问路在何方，前辈曾说过所以我也会留心路旁的野花美，到了山顶，真有一凉亭很破，鸟粪与湿草的气味齁的也够呛，我有点后悔并想象对面山头应该才有我想要的，天色渐晚我也快累瘫了，我想就在这破山头凑合着混，反正哪里也都是凑合。", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 913549}, {"id": 240660, "content": "悲剧的我并没有，也许以后会开个小店？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1150334}, {"id": 240661, "content": "小学作文里。\n我要当科学家！\n我要当明星！", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1039682}, {"id": 240662, "content": "以我的能力，这个就不必了吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1125639}, {"id": 240663, "content": "\n\n有非常明确的目标\n虽然不知道有一天会不会突然不喜欢了\n但现在在努力着", "image": "img/option/option/20171009131643j0M98BvUysVWOkSJ", "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1128828}, {"id": 240664, "content": "一直想创业，现在还在读大学，但是好迷茫，感觉很遥远，实际上也不过是两年后的事了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1148637}, {"id": 240665, "content": "从没认真做过，总是走一步看一步。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1150342}, {"id": 240666, "content": "大三了 至今迷茫不知道以后干什么  因为学的生物专业 不喜欢 唉", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1133121}, {"id": 240667, "content": "马上就要面临就业了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1146248}, {"id": 240668, "content": "我的职业规划是：啥赚钱干啥", "image": null, "praise_count": 50, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 253159}, {"id": 240669, "content": "基本是间歇性踌躇满志的时候会有热血规划，过了那个阶段后就忘记规划是什么了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1133429}, {"id": 240670, "content": "只在面试的时候说说，不过现在也还没到第一个时间节点\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 651076}, {"id": 240671, "content": "怎么赚钱怎么规划", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 785316}, {"id": 246303, "content": "后悔药，一直寻找ing", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1174851}, {"id": 240672, "content": "我一直在想\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1149297}, {"id": 240673, "content": "很希望自己可以认真地做职业规划这件事情，但是，突然发现自己不知该如何开始", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1126036}, {"id": 240674, "content": "社会膨胀，通货膨胀，自我膨胀。只有工作连职业都谈不上。无法在工作中找到归属感，职业规划只能搁浅了。", "image": "img/option/option/20171009140437OuMCSnzoW36U0Ixk.jpg", "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1142038}, {"id": 240676, "content": "不主动去了解，也就随意了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1119194}, {"id": 241188, "content": "准备面试的时候用", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1152529}, {"id": 240677, "content": "疲于奔命而已，不放松、不懈怠可以吧，先这样吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1117529}, {"id": 241189, "content": "曾经有过", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1152540}, {"id": 240678, "content": "只有在HR问到并要求我回答的时候想过", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1143265}, {"id": 240679, "content": "高中有过职业生涯规划课，好像没什么卵用，都是走一步看一步", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147386}, {"id": 240681, "content": "迷茫迷茫", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1150411}, {"id": 240937, "content": "至今不懂，至今待业", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 805712}, {"id": 240938, "content": "规划个鸡脖", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 805712}, {"id": 240683, "content": "没什么职业发展规划。毕竟还是单身，一人吃饱，全家不愁人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1226893}, {"id": 240684, "content": "不知道自己真正喜欢什么和适合什么职业，不知道从何开始规划", "image": "img/option/option/201710091434098HPIwkaAG2jnLxTo.jpg", "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1129963}, {"id": 240940, "content": "很想有，却对未来感到迷茫，正在解决ing", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1151334}]}